          While size does a lot of things "size wise" it actually never touches the width. 
          Furthermore for both {{#link-to 'shared-width-height'}}<code>width</code>{{/link-to}} and 
          {{#link-to 'shared-width-height'}}<code>height</code>{{/link-to}} there are times where you want
